data.description: Beautiful interior lot within Rolling Hills of Carefree - incredible Sunset and Mountain Views! Heated Salt Water Infinity Pool for year-round enjoyment adds to the perfect backyard for entertaining or relaxation! Large Covered Patio, Auto Sunshade, Putting Green, Built in BBQ, and Kiva Fireplace. Greatroom w/ built-in Entertainment Center, Fireplace, Wetbar & Wine Frig. Formal Dining Area. Updated Kitchen with Breakfast Bar and Walk-In Pantry. Owners Suite features Bay Window, Patio Exit, Fireplace, massive Walk-in Closet, Dual Sinks, Vanity Area, Jetted Tub, Snail Shower. Split Layout: 2 Guest Bedrooms with Jack and Jill Bath; plus Den/Office. 3 Car Garage w/ Storage and Epoxy Floors. Paver Drive/Walkways. $24k AC w/HEPA filter carbon UV air purifier; Water Softener, Roof re-coat 2019 Home wired for surround sound.
